\id 2TI New Alpha - June 11, 2007
\h 2 TIMOTEO
\toc3 2Ti
\toc2 2 Timoteo
\toc1 RI UKABꞌ WUJ RI XUTZꞌIBꞌAJ RI PABLO CHE RI TIMOTEO
\mt1 RI UKABꞌ WUJ RI XUTZꞌIBꞌAJ RI PABLO CHE RI TIMOTEO
\imt2 Majibꞌal re
\ip Ri Pablo xuya kanoq ri rachiꞌl Timoteo pa ri tinimit Éfeso rech jeriꞌ kachakun kukꞌ ri jujun kꞌamal taq bꞌe re ri komontyox ri man keniman taj. Ri Timoteo are xuriq kꞌax, ri Pablo xtzalij pa Éfeso.
\ip Ri Pablo are kꞌo pa cheꞌ pa ri tinimit Roma, xutzꞌibꞌaj apanoq che ri Timoteo chi rajawaxik kuchajij ribꞌ che ri Alejandro rumal che ri Alejandro xubꞌan kꞌax che ri Pablo are xkꞌojiꞌ chilaꞌ pa Éfeso. Ri Pablo xusikꞌij apanoq ri Timoteo rech kape chusolixik.
\ip Ri Pablo xubꞌij chike ri Figelo rachiꞌl ri Hermógenes chi man kakibꞌan ta chi ri kꞌamoj bꞌe, man xkita ta kꞌut ri xbꞌix chike xane xkibꞌan kikꞌulel che ri Pablo.
\ip E kꞌo xuqujeꞌ nikꞌaj winaq chik xkibꞌan kachiꞌl chike ri man keniman taj xeꞌkimenkꞌetij ri winaq rech kakijelechꞌuj ri kibꞌe rech are kakilij ubꞌanik ri tijoj chuqꞌabꞌ pa tzij xuqujeꞌ man keniman taj, rech keꞌl kanoq pa ri kꞌaslemal re chꞌajchꞌojil xuqujeꞌ nimanik. Ri Timoteo xkꞌistaj ukꞌuꞌx xuqujeꞌ xuxiꞌj ribꞌ, rumal riꞌ ri Pablo pa ri uwuj kuya chuqꞌabꞌ rech kabꞌan takꞌalem pa ri kojobꞌal rech ri utz laj tzij pune kakam jun rumal we riꞌ. Ri Pablo xuqujeꞌ kunaꞌtaj che ri Timoteo chi are kanaqajir loq ri qꞌij re ri upetibꞌal ri Jesús ri kape na jetaq jun nim taqanel, kepe na kꞌaxkꞌolal, kepe na esal taq kiwach ri e qꞌalajisal taq utzij ri Dios, bꞌanal taq tzij taq winaq, kꞌaxkꞌolal are waꞌ ri kuya na qꞌatebꞌal chike ri e kojonelabꞌ che ri Dios. Ri Pablo kutaqchiꞌj ri Timoteo rech kanaꞌtaj che ri utz laj tzij are chi ri Jesús ri \w Rijaꞌl ri David\w* xkꞌastaj chikixoꞌl ri kaminaqibꞌ xuqujeꞌ kuqꞌalajisaj ri tyoxalaj wuj ri retaꞌmam ri Timoteo pa ri ralkꞌaꞌlal are waꞌ katoꞌw na chubꞌanik ri utz laj chak.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Ri Pablo, taqoꞌn rech ri Cristo Jesús rumal ri rayibꞌal ukꞌuꞌx ri Dios, rumal ri kꞌaslemal ri chiꞌtal loq, ri yaꞌtal chaqe pa Cristo Jesús,
\v 2 che ri loqꞌalaj nukꞌojol Timoteo: Are ri Tataxel Dios xuqujeꞌ ri Cristo Jesús ri Ajawxel cheyoꞌw toqꞌobꞌ, toqꞌobꞌisan wach, xuqujeꞌ jaꞌmaril chawe.
\s1 Tzijonem chirij ri jeqelem
\p 
\v 3 Are katnaꞌtaj chwe chi paqꞌij chi chaqꞌabꞌ pa ri nuchꞌawem, kintyoxin che ri Dios, ri kinpatanij rukꞌ chꞌajchꞌoj laj chomabꞌal jacha ri xkibꞌan ri watiꞌt numam ojer.
\v 4 Xuqujeꞌ are kanaꞌtaj ri uwaꞌl awach chwe, are xinel loq, kawaj katinwil chi junmul, rech kinnoj che kiꞌkotemal.
\v 5 Xuqujeꞌ kanaꞌtaj chwe ri akojobꞌal ri qas ko kꞌolik, ri xutaqchiꞌj nabꞌe ri awatiꞌt Loida xuqujeꞌ ri anan Eunice, chanim kꞌut tajin katutaqchiꞌj at. Qas wetaꞌm chi jewaꞌ tajin kakꞌulmatajik.
\p 
\v 6 Rumal waꞌ kawaj chi kakꞌasbꞌaꞌ ri usipanik ri Dios, ri xakꞌamawaꞌj are xinya ri nuqꞌabꞌ pa awiꞌ.
\v 7 Rumal cher ri Dios man xuya taj jun uxlabꞌal rech xibꞌin ibꞌ chaqe, xane jun rech kwinem, loqꞌanik, xuqujeꞌ uj kujchoman ri kaqabꞌano.
\v 8 Xaq jeriꞌ man kakꞌixibꞌej ta uqꞌalajisaxik ri Ajawxel, xuqujeꞌ man kakꞌixibꞌej ta nubꞌixik in, rumal xa rumal rech ri Cristo in tzꞌapital pa cheꞌ. Je xuqujeꞌ ri at, rajawaxik rukꞌ ri ukwinem ri Dios, kakochꞌ ri kꞌaxkꞌolal rumal ri utz laj tzij.
\v 9 Rumal cher ri Dios xujukolo xuqujeꞌ xuya sikꞌinik chaqe pa ri jun tyoxalaj kꞌaslemal, man xa ta rumal ri qachak, xane rumal ri utoqꞌobꞌ xuqujeꞌ ri uchaꞌnik loq. Xuya loq we toqꞌobꞌ chaqe pa Cristo Jesús, are majaꞌ kamajitaj loq ri qꞌotaj.
\v 10 Kamik kꞌut xuqꞌalajisaj rukꞌ ri upetibꞌal ri qakolonel Cristo Jesús, ri xutukij ri kamikal xuqujeꞌ xukꞌam la pa ri tunal, ri kꞌaslemal ri man sachel ta uwach, rumal ri utz laj tzij.
\p 
\v 11 In xinux taqoꞌn, ajtij, xuqujeꞌ tzijol rech we tzij riꞌ.
\v 12 Rumal waꞌ kinriq kꞌax. Man kinkꞌix ta kꞌut rumal cher wetaꞌm jachin che in kojoninaq wi, xuqujeꞌ kuꞌl na kꞌuꞌx chi kꞌo ukwinem chinuyakik pa ri kꞌisbꞌal qꞌij, ri wayeꞌm.
\p 
\v 13 Chatereneꞌj ri kꞌutuꞌn ri xawetaꞌmaj wukꞌ, rukꞌ kojobꞌal xuqujeꞌ loqꞌanik pa Cristo Jesús.
\v 14 Chachajij ri jeꞌl laj kꞌutuꞌn rukꞌ ri ukwinem ri Tyoxalaj Uxlabꞌixel, ri kꞌo pa qanimaꞌ.
\p 
\v 15 Awetaꞌm chi konojel ri keꞌl pa taq ri tinimit rech Asia xinkitzaq kanoq, e kachiꞌl ri Figelo xuqujeꞌ ri Hermógenes.
\v 16 Are bꞌa ri Dios toqꞌobꞌisan kiwach ri winaq ri e kꞌo pa rachoch ri Onesíforo, rumal kꞌi mul, xinkitaqchiꞌj, man xekꞌix ta chwe, pune in kꞌo pa cheꞌ.
\v 17 Xuqujeꞌ are xopan pa ri tinimit Roma, xinutzukuj kꞌa xinuriq na.
\v 18 Are bꞌa ri Ajawxel chutoqꞌobisaj kiwach pa ri qꞌij rech chilaꞌ chikaj. Awetaꞌm ronojel ri patanijik ri xubꞌan wukꞌ pa ri tinimit Éfeso.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Xaq jeriꞌ nukꞌojol, chakꞌamawaꞌj achuqꞌabꞌ rumal ri toqꞌobꞌ ri kꞌo qukꞌ pa Cristo.
\v 2 Ri atom, nubꞌim chkiwach e kꞌi winaq, chaꞌtaqchiꞌj ri kojonelabꞌ e kuꞌlibꞌal taq kuꞌx, xuqujeꞌ qas kꞌo ketaꞌmabꞌal chukꞌutik chkiwach nikꞌaj winaq chik.
\p 
\v 3 Chatzijoj ri kꞌax ri qariqom, jeꞌ jas jun ajchꞌoꞌj chajil tinimit, rech ri Cristo.
\v 4 Maj jun ajchꞌoꞌj chajil tinimit kaqaj choch ri kꞌamal ubꞌe, we are keꞌ ukꞌuꞌx rukꞌ ri jastaq rech ri leꞌaj ri kel wi.
\v 5 Je xuqujeꞌ man kꞌo ta jun winaq ri kok pa jun tijoj anim, kukꞌamawaꞌj ri korona we man kunimaj ri kubꞌij ri taqanik rech ri etzꞌanem.
\v 6 Ri ajchak ri sibꞌalaj kachakunik yaꞌtal bꞌe che kukꞌamawaꞌj rech nabꞌe, ri yakoj.
\v 7 Qas chachomaj rij we kinbꞌij chawe, ri Ajawxel kꞌut katutoꞌ chuchꞌobꞌik waꞌ we riꞌ.
\p 
\v 8 Man kattaniꞌ ta che unaꞌtaxik ri Jesucristo, \w rijaꞌl ri David\w*, ri xwaꞌjilisax chikixoꞌl ri kaminaqibꞌ. Are waꞌ ri utz laj taq tzij.
\v 9 Rumal rech in jatꞌitalik jacha jun bꞌanal kꞌax. Ri utzij ri Dios kꞌut man jatꞌital taj.
\v 10 Kinkochꞌ kꞌu ronojel ri qꞌoxomal kumal ke ri e chaꞌtalik. Rech xuqujeꞌ koꞌpan pa ri koltajem ri kajuluwik ri maj ukꞌisik, ri yaꞌtal chaqe pa Cristo.
\v 11 Qas tzij wi we tzij riꞌ:
\m We kujkam rukꞌ ri Cristo,
\m kujkꞌasiꞌ xuqujeꞌ na rukꞌ.
\v 12 We kaqachuqꞌabꞌej, kujtaqan kꞌu na rukꞌ,
\m we kaqabꞌij chi man qetaꞌm ta uwach
\m Areꞌ xuqujeꞌ kubꞌij na chi man retaꞌm ta qawach.
\v 13 We man kujjeqiꞌ pa ri kaqabꞌij,
\m Areꞌ kajeqiꞌ wi pa ri utzij,
\m man kakwin taj kukꞌekꞌej ribꞌ.
\s1 Ri ajchak ri qas kaqaj cho ri Dios
\p 
\v 14 Man kattaniꞌ ta che unaꞌtaxik we riꞌ chike ri kojonelabꞌ. Chabꞌij chike man kakiya ta bꞌe che taq ri tzijitzatem ri maj kutayij, rumal xaq xwi kuꞌtukij ri ketowik.
\v 15 Chabꞌana ri achuqꞌabꞌ, rech katqaj cho ri Dios, jeꞌ jas jun ajchak ri maj kukꞌixibꞌej, ri kakwinik sukꞌ kuqꞌaxaj ri tzij rech qas tzij.
\v 16 Chaqꞌila awibꞌ chubꞌixik kꞌi taq tzij ri man tyoxalaj taq tzij taj, rumal ri jewaꞌ kakibꞌano, tajin kenajtin che ri utz laj bꞌe,
\v 17 xuqujeꞌ ri itzel taq kikꞌutuꞌn tajin kajabꞌunik jer kꞌo jun yabꞌil. Chikixoꞌl we winaq riꞌ e kꞌo ri Himeneo rachiꞌl ri Fileto,
\v 18 aꞌre waꞌ ri kiqꞌatom kibꞌ che ri qas tzij. Tajin kakibꞌij chi xkꞌulmataj ri kꞌastajibꞌal kiwach ri kaminaqibꞌ, kakimenkꞌetij kꞌu ri kojobꞌal kech e jujun.
\v 19 Pune jewaꞌ kakꞌulmatajik, ri utakꞌalibꞌal ri Dios sibꞌalaj ko kꞌolik, rumal cher kojtal retal rukꞌ we tzꞌibꞌatalik riꞌ: \qt Retaꞌm ri Ajawxel konojel ri e rech.\qt* We jun chik riꞌ kubꞌij: \qt Ri winaq ri kuqꞌijilaꞌj ri ubꞌiꞌ ri Ajawxel, chuqꞌila ribꞌ che ri mak.\qt*\x + \xo 2:19 \xt Números 16:5.\x*
\p 
\v 20 Pa jun nimalaj ja man xwi ta kꞌo qumubꞌal ri bꞌantal che qꞌana pwaq, xuqujeꞌ saqa pwaq, xane kꞌo xuqujeꞌ bꞌantal che, cheꞌ xuqujeꞌ kꞌo bꞌantal che ulew, kꞌo are kupatanij che ri jastaq ri nim uqꞌij, kꞌo xuqujeꞌ are kakoj che ri jastaq ri man nim ta uqꞌij.
\v 21 We kꞌu kꞌo jun kukꞌaslebꞌej jun chꞌajchꞌoj laj kꞌaslemal, kuxik jun jeꞌl laj kꞌolibꞌal, tyoxirisatalik, kꞌo kutayij che ri Ajawxel, xuqujeꞌ kakwinik kubꞌan utz laj taq chak.
\p 
\v 22 Chatanimajok choch ri rayinik rech alkꞌaꞌlal, are chabꞌana achuqꞌabꞌ chatereneꞌj ri sukꞌal, ri kojobꞌal, ri loqꞌanik, xuqujeꞌ ri jaꞌmaril, kukꞌ ri kakinaꞌtaj ri ubꞌiꞌ ri Ajawxel rukꞌ jun chꞌajchꞌoj laj animaꞌaj.
\v 23 Man kanim ta awibꞌ pa taq tzijonem ri maj kutayij, awetaꞌm chi chꞌoꞌj kakꞌisbꞌen rech ronojel.
\v 24 Xuqujeꞌ maj jun patanil rech ri Ajawxel ri xaq chꞌoꞌj karilij, xane rajawaxik utz kanoꞌjin kukꞌ konojel, kakwinik kuya kꞌutuꞌn, man aninaq taj kayojtajik.
\v 25 Xaq jeriꞌ rukꞌ mochꞌochꞌem, chaꞌsukꞌumaj ri e kꞌulel, kuꞌl akꞌuꞌx che ri Dios rech kubꞌan chike chi kakikꞌex kikꞌuꞌx, rech kaketaꞌmaj ri qas tzij.
\v 26 Rech kekꞌastajik xuqujeꞌ man keqaj ta pa ri kꞌaꞌmabꞌal jawjeꞌ ri kuꞌtzꞌapij wi ri Itzel, rech kakibꞌan ri urayibꞌal ukꞌuꞌx.
\c 3
\s1 Ri etzelal ri kabꞌan na pa ri kꞌisbꞌal taq qꞌij
\p 
\v 1 Kamik kꞌut, kꞌol pa ajolom chi kape na kꞌax taq qꞌotaj pa taq ri kꞌisbꞌal taq qꞌij.
\v 2 Ri winaq kenoj na xaq che uloqꞌaxik kibꞌ aꞌreꞌ xuqujeꞌ che kꞌarkꞌatem. Kakinaꞌ na nimal rukꞌ ri kakibꞌano, kakinimarisaj na kibꞌ, man keniman ta che ri kitat kinan, man ketyoxin taj, man kakikoj ta ri kabꞌix chike, xaq are kakichomaj na rij ri pwaq,
\v 3 maj kinaꞌoj, kꞌax kenoꞌjin na, bꞌanal taq tzij, kakibꞌan ri etzelal maj keqꞌatenik, man winaq taj kenoꞌjinik, uꞌkꞌulel ri utzilal,
\v 4 kakibꞌan bꞌanoj tzij chikij ri e kachiꞌl, xaq e tzukul taq chꞌoꞌj, kakibꞌan ri jastaq ri maj kutayij. Are sibꞌalaj kakiloqꞌoqꞌej ri mak, man kakiloqꞌaj ta kꞌu ri Dios.
\v 5 Kakijaluj na chi e utz taq winaq, rukꞌ kꞌu ri kichak kakiqꞌalajisaj chi xaq e bꞌanal taq tzij. Man kanim ta awibꞌ kukꞌ taq we winaq riꞌ.
\p 
\v 6 Jeriꞌ kenoꞌjin ri keꞌl cho taq ri ja, keꞌkimenkꞌetij ri ixoqibꞌ ri man kꞌax ta kitaqchiꞌxik pa mak, ri kꞌo itzel taq kirayinik.
\v 7 Amaqꞌel tajin keꞌtaꞌmanik, man kekwin ta kꞌu wi kaketaꞌmaj uwach ri qas tzij.
\v 8 Man kakiya ta bꞌe ketaꞌmax ri qas tzij, jacha ri xkibꞌan ri Janes xuqujeꞌ ri Jambres, xkikꞌopij kibꞌ choch ri xubꞌij ri Moisés, itzel taq kichomabꞌal, man utz taj kenoꞌjin pa ri kojobꞌal.\f + \fr 3:8 \ft Janes rachiꞌl Jambres are waꞌ kibꞌiꞌ e kebꞌ achyabꞌ ri kakesaj uwach kebꞌ oxibꞌ jastaq ri xubꞌan ri Moisés ojer are xopan rukꞌ ri Faraón. \xt Éxodo 7:10-13.\xt*\f*
\v 9 Man naj ta kꞌut kekꞌasiꞌ we winaq, we jewaꞌ kenoꞌjinik, rumal cher kiꞌl na kumal ri winaq chi maj ketaꞌmabꞌal, jacha ri xkꞌulmataj kukꞌ we kebꞌ achyabꞌ riꞌ.
\s1 Ri uchilabꞌ ri Pablo che ri Timoteo
\p 
\v 10 At kꞌut, are atereneꞌm pa ucholajil ri na kꞌutuꞌn, ri nubꞌanom che ukꞌaslebꞌexik ri nukꞌaslemal, ri kurayibꞌej na kꞌuꞌx, ri nukojobꞌal, ri kinbꞌan che rayeꞌxik ri jastaq, ri nuloqꞌanik, ri qꞌotaj nuqꞌiꞌom ubꞌanik ri jastaq.
\v 11 Ri kabꞌan chubꞌanik kꞌax chwe, ri kꞌaxkꞌolal ri kinriqo. Awetaꞌm ri kꞌaxkꞌolal ri xinriq pa ri tinimit Antioquía, pa Iconio, xuqujeꞌ pa Listra, xuqujeꞌ ri kꞌax ri xinqꞌiꞌo. Xuqujeꞌ che ronojel ri kꞌaxkꞌolal ri man xraj ta ri Dios, xinriqo.
\v 12 Xaq jeriꞌ kabꞌan kꞌu na kꞌax chike ri kakaj kakikꞌaslebꞌej jun utz laj kꞌaslemal pa Cristo Jesús.
\v 13 Are kꞌu ri itzel taq winaq ri keꞌkimenkꞌetij chi nikꞌaj, kenimataj riꞌ pa ri etzelal, keꞌkimenkꞌetij chi na nikꞌaj chik, xuqujeꞌ kemenkꞌetitaj na aꞌreꞌ.
\p 
\v 14 Ri at kꞌut, ko chatkꞌol pa ri awetaꞌmam, xuqujeꞌ chupam ri qas uchapom wi akꞌuꞌx, rumal cher awetaꞌm jachin kukꞌ awetaꞌmam wi.
\v 15 Pa ri awalkꞌaꞌlal awetaꞌmam ri kꞌo pa ri Tyoxalaj tzꞌibꞌatalik, are waꞌ kayoꞌw awetaꞌmabꞌal ri kajawataj che ri akolotajem rumal ri kojobꞌal pa Cristo Jesús.
\v 16 Ronojel ri tzꞌibꞌatalik pa we wuj riꞌ utzij ri Dios, xuqujeꞌ utz kakꞌutik, rech kuꞌl ri winaq pa ri uchomabꞌal, rech qas utz kanoꞌjinik, rech kasukꞌumax ri winaq, xuqujeꞌ kapixibꞌax jun pa ri sukꞌal.
\v 17 Rech ri rajchak ri Dios, qas kakꞌojiꞌ retaꞌmabꞌal che ubꞌanik utz taq chak.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Kinchilibꞌej chawe qas cho ri Dios rachiꞌl ri Cristo Jesús, ri kape na pa ri rajawarem xuqujeꞌ kuqꞌat na tzij pa kiwiꞌ ri e kꞌaslik xuqujeꞌ ri e kaminaqibꞌ.
\v 2 Chatzijoj ri utzij ri Dios, are chawilij amaqꞌel, we kꞌu are uqꞌotaj o man are ta neꞌ, chaꞌtaqchiꞌj chi nikꞌaj, man katyojtaj ta aninaq, man kattaniꞌ ta che uyaꞌik kꞌutuꞌn.
\v 3 Rumal cher kꞌu ri qa na qꞌij ri man kakꞌamawaꞌx ta chi ri utz laj kꞌutuꞌn, xane keꞌkꞌam bꞌik rumal ri urayibꞌal kikꞌuꞌx, kebꞌe kukꞌ aꞌjtijabꞌ che utatabꞌexik ri qꞌolobꞌal ri kakaj kakito.
\v 4 Ketaniꞌ na che utatabꞌexik ri qas tzij, ketzalij kan chutatabꞌexik ri jastaq ri man tzij taj.
\v 5 At kꞌut, qas chachajij awibꞌ pa ronojel ri jastaq ri kakꞌulmatajik, chaqꞌiꞌaꞌ ri kꞌax, are chawilij utzijoxik ri utzij ri Dios, utz chabꞌana che ri achak ri xuya ri Dios.
\p 
\v 6 Are kꞌu ri in, xuriq ri qꞌotaj kinkamisaxik jacha jun sipanik, xuqujeꞌ xuriq ri qꞌotaj rech ri nubꞌenam.
\v 7 Xinchꞌoꞌjij ri utz laj chꞌoꞌj, xintoꞌtaj che ri nuchak, xinjeqiꞌ pa ri nukojobꞌal.
\v 8 Xaq jeriꞌ in rayeꞌm ri korona rech sukꞌal, pa ri kꞌisbꞌal qꞌij, ri kuya na ri Ajawxel, sukꞌalaj qꞌatal tzij. Man xaq xwi ta kꞌu in kaya we, xane kaya ke konojel ri kakayeꞌj apanoq ri upetibꞌal.
\s1 Ri chilabꞌ ri kabꞌan che ri Timoteo
\p 
\v 9 Chabꞌana toqꞌobꞌ chatpet chiwilik aninaq.
\v 10 Ri Demas, rumal uloqꞌaxik ri jastaq rech uwachulew, xinutzaq kanoq, xeꞌ pa ri tinimit Tesalónica. Ri Crescente xeꞌ pa ri tinimit Galacia, xuqujeꞌ ri Tito xeꞌ pa ri tinimit Dalmacia.
\v 11 Xaq xwi ri Lucas kꞌo wukꞌ. Chakꞌama loq ri Marcos rumal cher kꞌo kutayij chwe pa we chak riꞌ.
\v 12 Xintaq bꞌik ri Tíquico pa ri tinimit Éfeso.
\v 13 Are katpetik, chakꞌama loq ri nukaton ri xinya kan pa ri tinimit Troas, pa rachoch ri Carpo. Chakꞌama xuqujeꞌ loq ri nikꞌaj tzꞌuꞌm ri kꞌo tzꞌibꞌ choch.
\p 
\v 14 Ri Alejandro ri chꞌayal chꞌichꞌ, sibꞌalaj ubꞌanom kꞌax chwe, are bꞌa ri Dios katojow na ukꞌaxel che.
\v 15 Chachajij xuqujeꞌ awibꞌ at che, rumal cher xukꞌopij ribꞌ are xqatzijoj ri utz laj taq tzij che.
\p 
\v 16 Are xintoꞌ wibꞌ nabꞌe mul cho ri qꞌatbꞌal tzij, xa ta ne jun xinutoꞌo, xane konojel xinkitzaq kanoq. Mat bꞌa kakoj pa kwenta.
\v 17 Ri Ajawxel kꞌut xkꞌojiꞌ wukꞌ xuqujeꞌ xuya nuchuqꞌabꞌ, rech kintzijoj na ri utz laj tzij, rech kakita konojel ri winaq ri man aꞌj Israel taj. Ri Ajawxel xuqujeꞌ xinutoꞌo rech man xinkikamisaj ta ri winaq ri jer kenoꞌjin koj.
\v 18 Ri Ajawxel kinuchajij na che ronojel etzelal, xuqujeꞌ kinuyak na rech kinok rukꞌ pa ri rajawarem chilaꞌ chikaj. Che areꞌ yoꞌq wi juluwem chibꞌe qꞌij saq. Jeriꞌ.
\s1 Kꞌisbꞌal taq rutzil wach
\p 
\v 19 Chaya rutzil kiwach ri Priscila\f + \fr 4:19 \ft Prisca are jun ubꞌiꞌ chi ri Priscila. \xt Hechos 18:2.\xt*\f* xuqujeꞌ ri Aquila, je xuqujeꞌ ri Onesíforo.
\v 20 Ri Erasto xkanaj kan pa ri tinimit Corinto. Are kꞌu ri Trófimo, xinya kan pa ri tinimit Mileto rumal cher yawabꞌ.
\v 21 Chabꞌana toqꞌobꞌ chatpet kan pa taq ri qꞌij are majaꞌ kuchapleꞌj ri qꞌalaj. Kakitaq bꞌik rutzil awach ri Eubulo, ri Pudente, ri Lino, ri Claudia, xuqujeꞌ konojel ri alaxik.
\p 
\v 22 Are ri Ajawxel kakanaj pa ri awanimaꞌ. Are ri toqꞌobꞌ kakanaj iwukꞌ.
